msgctxt "Talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Curious, indeed. As it were, I perused\n"
"my teacher's old notes...and found\n"
"that song there.\n"
"<2.an>Hmm, what sort of sound could alarm\n"
"a horse so effectively?\n"
"\n"
"Kabam? Kapow? Rumble, rumble?\n"
"Honestly, I haven't a clue.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>It certainly helps to visit the locations\n"
"that inspired the song. Yes, it helps\n"
"open my mind to inspiration.\n"
"Those notes had other interesting\n"
"songs too... I plan to visit those\n"
"locations as well."
msgstr ""

